  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably from the end of July until Christmas Day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the factory where we work, it was a very-- place where we was horrible workers, because we tried to destroy everything we can.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because if they told us it was element we have to work with it, and we have to put screws and other kind of wires in this element, if we was told it has to be done at the right side, if we can, we did as many on the left side as it was possible.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Other things we did, we goes to the washroom, and we throw as many pieces into the washroom as we can.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Unfortunately, the washroom was, you know, flooded, and they find out this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They want to know who did this, and quite a few pay big price for this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a very clean factory, and it was like a chain work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Maybe ten of us sitting in one line, and you do this, this, and the next did something what he has to do.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was Germans foremans who was teaching us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You also have very, very fine machinery to making coals in certain element.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we start-- we got to get up 4:30 in the morning to get ready, before they count us all together.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we start at 7 o'clock in the factory with no food at all, because we only get food at night, after our work.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We have 12 hours work to do. 10 o'clock, we got some hot water or some kind of a tea.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We also have our lunch break, if you have something to eat, if you save something from the night before.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Otherwise, we wasn't hurt there, or any way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We was normally treated-- if you do your work.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
